{"tid":415211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曼德拉效應好似越來越嚴重(集思廣益)","createTime":"2017-09-26T20:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T08:05:51.000Z","uid":117597,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8da5066d7a0c489df004ba3f7b60a1aba5ea736e","tid":415211,"uid":117597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:16:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人有研究過 或睇過相關資料？<br />\n呢個世界發生緊咩事？<br />\n睇完youtube解說 好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347cc5867b7448852773cefc4fda16bb5312f621","tid":415211,"uid":4563,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:07:04.000Z","msg":"幻覺就幻覺啦，記錯就記錯啦。扮乜曼德拉效應"},{"pid":"61ec9d91155bd908b4d010de929f3c3576752e57","tid":415211,"uid":119896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人有研究過 或睇過相關資料？<br />\n呢個世界發生緊咩事？<br />\n睇完youtube解說 好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nlink？"},{"pid":"0bbe21a216e673b922e93c1c5eec4458d49faf1a","tid":415211,"uid":57962,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:19:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63ec7a2920e63d8e69a243747fbc126ff7be4b2b","tid":415211,"uid":60341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:07:16.000Z","msg":"其實有冇香港自己嘅曼德拉效應事件？<br />\n暫時見得多嘅都係香港人原本就一知半解嘅事<br />\n唔明點解要跟住啲鬼佬起哄"},{"pid":"8eab0773b6dc3f52dd309606fc269ea5eda217a4","tid":415211,"uid":55851,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇香港自己嘅曼德拉效應事件？<br />\n暫時見得多嘅都係香港人原本就一知半解嘅事<br />\n唔明點解要跟住啲鬼佬起哄</blockquote><br />\n香港人集體失憶第一次見？"},{"pid":"c22f2b25c727f5f46f5fff9d0b24976729d4fabe","tid":415211,"uid":5616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T02:31:24.000Z","msg":"曼波拉效應呀"},{"pid":"cfeaf34fbe73c6c1c9ac0ce70fd43114660d6467","tid":415211,"uid":59886,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":